, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary, I throw myself down among the tall grass by the trickling.\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eae5e16 cmsmasters-testimonial-layout-bottom cmsmasters-testimonial-author-width-inline cmsmasters-block-default cmsmasters-sticky-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-cmsmasters-testimonial\" data-id=\"eae5e16\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"cmsmasters-testimonial.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https:\/\/save-the-children.cmsmasters.net\/international-aid\/wp-content\/plugins\/cmsmasters-elementor-addon\/assets\/css\/widget-cmsmasters-testimonials.min.css\"><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Review\"><div class=\"elementor-screen-only\" itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Organization\">\n\t\t\t\t<meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"International Aid\">\n\t\t\t\t<link itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https:\/\/save-the-children.cmsmasters.net\/international-aid\" \/><\/div><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial__inner\"><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial__main-area\"><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial__content\"><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial__content-outer\"><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial__content-inner\"><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial__text\" itemprop=\"reviewBody\"><p>Hence a high-quality, all-embracing education is vitally important to fight child poverty. UNESCO expresses it remarkably succinctly, education transforms lives. Education gives everyone, regardless of financial status, the opportunity to prosper by nurturing hope for the future.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"cmsmasters-testimonial__author-info\"><div class=\"cmsm